com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.server
Interface ServerRoot

All Known Implementing Classes:
ServerRootImpl
public interface ServerRoot

A representation of the model object 'Root'.

The following features are supported:

  • Mixed
  • XMLNS Prefix Map
  • XSI Schema Location
  • Capability Server
  • Unit Server Unit
